author: Associated Press
title: China to end lockdown of coronavirus-hit Hubei province; Wuhan to open next month
description: Chinese authorities said Tuesday they will end a two-month lockdown of most of coronavirus-hit Hubei province at midnight, as domestic cases of the virus continue to subside.
